vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a new specific use permit for a paraphernalia shop on property zoned Planned Development District No. 810, on the northeast corner of North Cockrell Hill Road and I-30 Frontage Road
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval, subject to a site plan and staff’s recommended conditions
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval for a five-year period, subject to a site plan and conditions
Z-25-000081
